						<p>Incomplete. This inscription mentions the shrine of Akkasālaipiḷḷaiyār built on the bank of the tank called Poṉṉiūruṇi <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Pichchikuḻi in Tirukkōḷakkuḍi. Signatories like Karaiyūr Arasaṉ and Teṟkāṭṭūr Saḍaiyaṉ etc.</p>						

