<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> komāṟu paṉmarāṉa tiripu<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>ṉaccakaravatikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kulacekaratevaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="10"><g type="numeral">10</g></num><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>vatu <hi rend="grantha">pruści</hi>ka nāyaṟ
<lb n="2"/>ṟu <hi rend="grantha">Aparapakṣa</hi>ttu <hi rend="grantha">dvi</hi>tiyaiyum veḷḷikkiḻamaiyum peṟṟa rocaṉināḷ puṟamalaiṉāṭṭut tirukkoḷa
<lb n="3"/>kkuṭi Uṭaiya nāyaṉār tirukkoyilt tāṉattom Ivvūr poṉṉi Ūruṇiyāṉa picci kuḻikkarai
<lb n="4"/>yil Eḻuntaruḷi Irukkum Akkacālaippiḷḷaiyāṟku kalvāyūr nāṭṭuk kāḷaiyar kālapperunteruvi <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>2 karaiyūr virarācentirak kāṉa nāṭṭu ve <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>pāṇṭiyak kāṉaṉāṭṭu veḷāṉ Eḻuttu
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ramuṭaiyāṉ Eḻuttu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> I Ūr Aracaṉ Aracan Eḻuttu Ivvū
<lb n="8" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vayan Eḻuttu teṟkāṭṭur caṭaiyaṉ Aracu <hi rend="grantha">sajñ</hi>ai māṭ <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ṉūr veḷāṉ puṭṭaṉ celvañāṉacampan Eḻuttu Ivvūrp perumāḷ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kamuṭaiyāṉ Āṇṭapiḷḷaiyāna puka
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> maṉ kampaṉṉa Uttama coḻamārā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

